  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required credibility level due to a single test condition being exercised. This model has been applied in clinical research settings to inform implant design decisions, and the ensemble predictions have been shared with device sponsors for regulatory submissions. No structured Context of Use object is provided under this minimal-profile submission.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-construct-performance",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v1",
